    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="HTML之表单详解"><a href="#HTML之表单详解" class="headerlink" title="HTML之表单详解"></a>HTML之表单详解</h1><p><strong>表单：</strong>专门用来收集用户信息的。</p><p><strong>表单标签</strong>（即元素/标记）：比较特殊，有特殊的外观和默认的功能。</p><p><em>表单的格式：</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">表单元素</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h3 id="常见的表单元素："><a href="#常见的表单元素：" class="headerlink" title="常见的表单元素："></a>常见的表单元素：</h3><p><u>input标签：</u>它有一个type属性，这个属性有很多类型的取值，取值的不同就决定了input标签的功能和外观。</p><ol><li>明文输入框：</li></ol><p>内容：<code>&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot;&gt;</code></p><ol start="2"><li>暗文输入框：</li></ol><p>内容：<code>&lt;input type=&quot;password&quot;&gt;</code></p><ol start="3"><li>给输入框设置默认值：</li></ol><p>内容：<code>&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;123&quot;&gt;</code></p><ol start="4"><li>单选框：</li></ol><p>a.默认情况下单选框不会互斥，要想单选框互斥，那么必须给每一个单选框设置一个name属性，然后name属性还必须设置相同的值。</p><p>b.要想让单选框默认选中某一个框子，可以给input标签添加一个checked属性。</p><p>内容：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"radio"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"gender"</span> <span class="attr">checked</span>=<span class="string">"checked"</span>&gt;</span>内容1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"radio"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"gender"</span>&gt;</span>内容2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"radio"</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"gender"</span>&gt;</span>内容3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>小小理解：</strong>radio是收音机的意思，收音机永远只有一个按键被按下，其它弹起。</p><ol start="5"><li>多选框：</li></ol><p>内容：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"checkbox"</span>&gt;</span>内容1</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"checkbox"</span>&gt;</span>内容2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"checkbox"</span>&gt;</span>内容3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="6"><li>按钮：定义一个普通按钮，配合js完成一些简单操作。value属性指定按钮标题。</li></ol><p><code>&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;我是按钮&quot;&gt;</code></p><p>想要好看的按钮，就要用图片来定义按钮。</p><p><code>&lt;input type=&quot;image&quot; src=&quot;&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><strong>重置按钮：</strong>reset，有默认指定标题为“重置”，如果不想默认，也可以通过value属性来修改标题。</p><p>作用：用来清空表单中的数据。</p><p>内容：<code>&lt;input type=&quot;reset&quot; value=&quot;&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><strong>提交按钮：</strong>submit，也有默认标题。  </p><p>作用：将表单中的数据提交到远程服务器。</p><p>内容：<code>&lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; value=&quot;&quot;&gt;</code></p><p><strong>注意点：</strong>要想把表单中的数据提交到远程服务器，必须满足两个条件。</p><p>a、告诉表单需要提交到哪个服务器，form标签中的action属性可以告诉表单提交到哪个服务器。</p><p>b、告诉表单，表单中的哪些数据需要提交，添加name属性即可。</p><p><strong>隐藏域：</strong>用于悄悄咪咪收集用户的一些数据，它是不会出现在界面中的。</p><p>内容：<code>&lt;input type=&quot;hidden&quot; name=&quot;cc&quot; value=&quot;it666&quot;&gt;</code></p><p> 一点击提交按钮，地址栏中就会出现cc=it666。</p><ol start="7"><li>默认情况下文字和输入框是没有关联的，也就是说点击文字输入框不会聚焦，如果想点击文字时让对应的输入框聚焦，那么就需要让文字和输入框进行绑定。则使用<strong>label标签</strong>。</li></ol><p>如何使用？</p><p>第一步，给文字加label标签。</p><p>第二步，给对应输入框添加id属性。</p><p>第三步，给label标签添加for属性，属性值跟对应的id值一样，实现绑定。</p><p><em>例子：</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span> <span class="attr">for</span>=<span class="string">"aa"</span>&gt;</span>内容：<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"aa"</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还有一个更简单的方式：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">内容：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是它具有局限性，不能随机绑定任何输入框。</p><ol start="8"><li>datalist标签：给输入框绑定待定项。（仅作了解，因为很多浏览器不支持它。）</li></ol><p><em>例子：</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">内容：<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span> <span class="attr">list</span>=<span class="string">"cars"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">datalist</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"cars"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>宝马<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>奔驰<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>路虎<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">datalist</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
