    <title>HTML之表格标签</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2020/02/18/HTML%E4%B9%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2020/02/18/HTML%E4%B9%8B%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE/</id>
    <published>2020-02-18T09:56:06.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-02-18T12:24:51.456Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="HTML之表格标签"><a href="#HTML之表格标签" class="headerlink" title="HTML之表格标签"></a>HTML之表格标签</h2><h3 id="格式："><a href="#格式：" class="headerlink" title="格式："></a>格式：</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span>    //整个表格</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span>         //表格中的一行</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>需要显示的内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>     //一个单元格</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h3 id="表格标签的属性："><a href="#表格标签的属性：" class="headerlink" title="表格标签的属性："></a>表格标签的属性：</h3><ul><li><p>边框属性：border，这个属性决定了边框的高度，默认情况下这个属性的值为0，所以看不到边框。</p></li><li><p>宽度和高度的属性：可以给table标签和td标签使用。</p><p>1、表格的宽度和高度默认是按照内容的尺寸来调整的。</p><p>2、如果给td标签设置width/height属性，会修改当前单元格的宽高，并不会影响整个表格的宽高。</p></li><li><p>水平对齐（align）和垂直对齐（valign——“top/center/bottom”）的属性：其中水平对齐可以给table标签和tr标签和td标签使用，垂直对齐只能给tr和td标签使用。</p><p>1、给table标签设置align属性，可以控制表格在水平方向的对齐方式。</p><p>2、给tr标签设置align属性，可以控制当前行中所有单元格内容的对齐方式。</p><p>3、给td标签设置align属性，可以控制当前单元格中内容在水平方向的对齐方式。</p></li></ul><p><em>注意点：</em>如果td中设置了align属性，tr中也设置了align属性，那么单元格中的内容会按照td中设置的来对齐。</p><ul><li><p>外边距和内边距的属性：只能给table标签使用。</p><p>1、外边距就是单元格和单元格之间的距离。默认是cellspacing=”2”。</p><p>2、内边距就是单元格的边框和文字之间的间隙。默认是cellpadding=”1”</p></li><li><p>背景颜色（bgcolor）的属性：table/tr/td标签都可。</p></li></ul><h2 id="关于表格还有其他标签："><a href="#关于表格还有其他标签：" class="headerlink" title="关于表格还有其他标签："></a>关于表格还有其他标签：</h2><p>1、表格标题：caption 是写在表格标签里面的，属于表格标签的一部分。</p><p>例子：</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>表格标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">......</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2、标题单元格（表头）：th标签，每一列的标题。  </p><p>作用：自动居中+文字加粗。一般把第一行的所有td都换成th。</p><p><strong>表格中的存储的数据分为四类：</strong></p><p>a.表格的标题   b.表格的表头信息   c.表格的主体信息   d.表格的页尾信息</p><p><em>表格的完整结构表示：</em>（企业开发中不需要这么写，仅作了解。）</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span>表格的标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">caption</span>&gt;</span>     ——表格的标题</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span>              ——表格的表头信息</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>每一列的标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">thead</span>&gt;</span>       ——表格的主体信息</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>数据<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tfoot</span>&gt;</span>       ——表格的页尾信息</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>数据<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tfoot</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意点：</strong></p><p>如果我们没有编写tbody，系统会自动给我们添加tbody。</p><p>如果指定了thead和tfoot，那么在修改整个表格的高度时，thead和tfoot有自己默认的高度，不会随<br>着表格的高度变化而变化。</p><h2 id="单元格合并："><a href="#单元格合并：" class="headerlink" title="单元格合并："></a>单元格合并：</h2><p>1、水平方向上的合并：colspan</p><p><code>&lt;td colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;</code></p><p>2、垂直方向上的合并：rowspan</p><p><code>&lt;td rowspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;/td&gt;</code></p><p>如何理解呢?</p><p>“2”，指的是把当前单元格当做两个单元格来对待。   </p><p><strong>注意：</strong>永远向后或者向下合并，记得删除多余的单元格。</p>]]></content>
    
