    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="HTML之列表标签"><a href="#HTML之列表标签" class="headerlink" title="HTML之列表标签"></a>HTML之列表标签</h1><h2 id="列表标签的分类"><a href="#列表标签的分类" class="headerlink" title="列表标签的分类"></a>列表标签的分类</h2><h3 id="一、无序列表（用得最多）（unordered-list）"><a href="#一、无序列表（用得最多）（unordered-list）" class="headerlink" title="一、无序列表（用得最多）（unordered list）"></a>一、无序列表（用得最多）（unordered list）</h3><p>用于一堆数据没有先后之分的情况下，自带小黑点。</p><a id="more"></a><p><em>格式：</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>需要显示的条目内容<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>    （list item英文名的缩写）</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ul</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>应用场景：新闻列表、商品列表（图文）、导航条。</p><h3 id="二、有序列表（用得最少）（ordered-list）"><a href="#二、有序列表（用得最少）（ordered-list）" class="headerlink" title="二、有序列表（用得最少）（ordered list）"></a>二、有序列表（用得最少）（ordered list）</h3><p>123456…..数据有先后之分。</p><p><em>格式：</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="三、定义列表（其次）（definition-list）"><a href="#三、定义列表（其次）（definition-list）" class="headerlink" title="三、定义列表（其次）（definition list）"></a>三、定义列表（其次）（definition list）</h3><p><em>格式：</em></p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span>   //definition title</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span>    //definition description</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>注意：</strong></p><p>虽然dd可多个，但是推荐一个dt对应一个dd。</p><p><u>应用场景：</u></p><p>做网站底部的相关信息、做图文混排。</p>]]></content>
    
